---
layout: default
title: Media
---
<div class="mb-10 prose max-w-none">
    This is a collection of videos and podcasts where I participate.

    All my recorded conference talks that are available on YouTube can be found in
    <a href="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLNSXqfC0E8JnI8fbfM77hz9_gOQKpgjdL" target="_new">a playlist.</a>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-wrap -mx-2">
    {% for item in media %}
    <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 md:w-1/3 self-stretch p-2 mb-2">
        <div class="rounded shadow-md h-full">
            <a href="{{ item.url | url }}" target="_new">
                {% videoThumbnail item, "w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto" %}
                <div class="px-6 py-5">
                    <div class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">
                        {{ item.title }}
                    </div>
                    <div class="italic text-lg mb-2">
                        {{ item.occasion }}
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-1" title="Published date">{{ item.date }}</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-800">
                        {% if item.description %}
                        {{ item.description }}
                        {% endif %}
                    </p>
                </div>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
</div>